{"tid":1650471,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔應該將人權法睇咁重，應該視為bonus，唔係抗爭主手段","createTime":"2019-10-13T03:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T06:32:35.000Z","uid":194415,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f98755b9cef156fa56b94aa06d752ebfb247b8c2","tid":1650471,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:34:19.000Z","msg":"依家美國都大亂<br />\n烏克蘭 同 庫德軍 兩單野（自己去 reddit 睇下）未計競選未找數 ...<br />\n已經令 trump 幾乎同所有人都反晒面<br />\n人權法 &ldquo;實際作用&rdquo; 未必會影響到局勢（因為拖太耐，對家都準備好晒承受所有後果）<br />\n<br />\n依家感覺太多人都 倚賴晒 人權法（尤其是 40+ 以上果班 ...）<br />\n覺得一通過人權法香港就有轉機<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係嫁！千奇沉醉係幻想！</span><br />\n<br />\n就算依家即時有 [獨立調查委員會]<br />\n都唔一定出到真相嫁<br />\n因為 實際點運作 冇人知！可以係有實質作用，可以不了了之<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">充滿希望 就有 大失所望</span>"},{"pid":"0f56f4d6e1fe4c1fd599325f063399cc887272a1","tid":1650471,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:48:03.000Z","msg":"同時，國際上真係多左人支持香港（不論有咩目的）<br />\n好多人都感受到中國威脅，例：想 boycott mic 產品都好難 ...<br />\n香港有 ＄12 店算係幾好，至少有部份野可以買 mij<br />\n亦都開始回望過去自己身邊事物有幾多比中國操控晒"},{"pid":"4e9ce6b3c583962fa5ede26d1e44eaecdc2ee7c7","tid":1650471,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KnAJUrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnAJUrV.jpg&h=222a48c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>10.13 10.14 不見不散</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c715fa25191b2ead8c44c7d074cd3f5728f0f1a5","tid":1650471,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:45:16.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"579e28281f405c08e576d56409df37b5eb178871","tid":1650471,"uid":244357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"